{"tid":2388486,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講定先　國難當前　大舉「移民」到另一國家　別國大眾往後會點睇","createTime":"2021-01-31T07:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T09:14:10.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1335ef2eec005133e0ce547fb377b01d728a94d8","tid":2388486,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158893399282357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158893399282357&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWnG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=cc130adc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158893399282357</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人最愛說的是移民，可惜大部分都了解不到，移民的根本性質，是建立一個公民身份，取其義務而換得權利與榮耀。如果只是想逃難，那就只是難民，別人會先可憐你再鄙視你，因為你根本無心承擔起社會與國家的存續。對於國家的未來並沒有用處。<br />\n<br />\n可憐你是因為你連公民權利也沒有，鄙視你是因為你也沒心去執行公民的義務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n江采蘋:<br />\n不少前線手足根本沒有bno(97後出生/ 新移民後代)，喊得最大聲的當中一大堆freerider。起因是反送中之後英國政府決定放寬BNO的居留限制，玻璃心強國就在那邊講沒有用不承認之類的，然後一堆「國際線」youtuber、促統黨又跟著靠腰拚kpi而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_J0O9zYyiQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_J0O9zYyiQU&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWnG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=7f0fdf6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_J0O9zYyiQU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzLN9Sn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzLN9Sn.jpg&h=13a94bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《葛量洪回憶錄：尋找蝗蟲問題的前世今生》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2012/02/20/3244/葛量洪回憶錄：尋找蝗蟲問題的前世今生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2012%2F02%2F20%2F3244%2F%E8%91%9B%E9%87%8F%E6%B4%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E9%8C%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E8%9D%97%E8%9F%B2%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%8A%E7%94%9F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWnG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=6c2386dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2012/02/20/3244/葛量洪回憶錄：尋找蝗蟲問題的前世今生</a><br />\n<br />\n英國人施捨他們的慈善，是因為他們貴族式的虛榮。看得透這種矛盾的民族性的人，又怎好意思像偽左和土共那樣單純地仇英、或是像坊間許多一般見識的人那樣完全的親英？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/elsa.au1/posts/1467989046561971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Felsa.au1%2Fposts%2F1467989046561971&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWnG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=9121bdf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/elsa.au1/posts/1467989046561971</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Elsa Au<br />\n<br />\n我幾十歲，都唔想移民!<br />\n除非我個仔話要移民啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYin Kwan Chau:<br />\n法治已死，係時候念下去第二度落腳<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n再講移民是無益的, 全世界都不想收難民, 到頭來要想的是怎樣勝利, 其他的都不用多想.<br />\n<br />\nElsa Au: 我根在此!<br />\n<br />\nMing Tse: 你有得移民己好幸福<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n將心比己，全世界都不歡迎蝗蟲，包括港蝗。正如我們都會，為何我要解決你們的問題，你們不解決你們地方的問題？"},{"pid":"47351832ef9c9a87ce237fbe70d2b3d208e2ce94","tid":2388486,"uid":112581,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"國難當前到底翻工癡線d定移民癡線d？<br />\n根本大部分香港人都唔覺得係國難<br />\n如果唔係就唔會大三罷都罷唔成"},{"pid":"5a23ba1d8c0a8f81be978c4c85edfecd721f6e8d","tid":2388486,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"你叫chenlap死番番黎香港先黎講野"},{"pid":"35f52326e44d8550366e455e03234e7a76936b43","tid":2388486,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"本黎係英藉，又點移民？"},{"pid":"d95d0708132474ff83426bda7ff09a74dd9f832e","tid":2388486,"uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35f52326e44d8550366e455e03234e7a76936b43","tid":2388486,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"本黎係英藉，又點移民？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"去中華民國，又算是移民嗎？"},{"pid":"2ee9afe0f0753d168cca7209fe92e6cd9